Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Hello, I am wondering if you give any ad credits for the new accounts ?

Hi there! Yes, we do offer ad credits for new accounts. Ad credits are a promotional form of payment for ads on NewsBreak. If you've received an ad credit and are wondering how to redeem it, you can follow the step-by-step instructions in this guide: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17391456255629-How-to-redeem-a-NewsBreak-ad-credit).
I am not sure I received one, can I get it?

Hi! If you're unsure whether you've received an ad credit, I recommend checking your account's billing section. If you haven't received one, you can contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com to inquire about the availability of ad credits for new accounts. Let me know if you need any further assistance!
